,Recommended,263060,31473635,Posted: 30 April,all,GamerPinoy,"Blockstorm is a first-person shooter set in a Minecraft-like universe. It combines both the fun aspects of any first person shooter, along with a satisfyingly destructible environment!The game offers a surprisingly in-depth customizer for both your character and weapons at hand. In addition to this, it provides a map editor to satisfy those itching creators!Not the creative type? No problem. A whole workshop full of community-made skins, weapons and maps are waiting to be downloaded!Looking at the gameplay, it contains 6 gamemodes (Deathmatch, Team DM, CTF, Assault, Castle Battle, Hunt) in which feel relatively the same but is still good for a change of gameplay.Looking at Blockstorm, it seems to contain a full package to be considered as a FPS, but time will tell if the devs will make further improvements to keep this game on top.7/10 (Great)"
