76561198079711894,Not Recommended,263060,29877031,Posted: 12 February,all,Zusheqiel,"I want to reccomend but I can't at this moment.First off as far as I can tell the devs have more or less abandoned the game, though I don't think it was by choice.The customization in this game is amazing, so props for that.There's no clan system as far as I can tell.When I move around in game it feels like I'm skating slowly on ice all the time. Sniping can be fun if you can get used to the drunk goggles simulator they have for the scope. Shotguns are typically one hit kills and are Ideal for close range, they're not heavy allowing you to move more quickly. Funny thing is 75% of the maps are more or less close range fighting leaving little choice to do else. The assault rifle is ehh ok for close range but better for mid range. The other guns are simply ok with ice skating type aiming.The game is more or less a kill fest for veterans, if you quit to get away from the massacre then you're a rage quitter. No win situation. It can be fun at times if the teams are ballanced, but most of the time it simply feels like an inconvenience."
