,Recommended,263060,20210280,"Posted: 2 January, 2016",all,MrExzibit,"Recommended17.6 hrs on recordDescriptionBlockstorm is a blocky and cartoony FPS game with a wide variety of maps, gamemodes, guns and other awesome features. The game is great with fantastic workshop creations made everyday. This game comes with a map editor and a weapon customizer which allows you to create your own very personal beasty looking gun, or if you're feeling lazy to make a weapon. You can pick and download from the thousands of already created weapon skins in the workshop so you can show off in battles! There's also a character creation tool fitted within the game so you're able to upload your character to the workshop! This means you are aloud full customization. So if you want to be a Pope with a giant pink RPG then you can sure as hell do that! Also, almost EVERYTHING is destroyable.What I think of the game?So Blockstorm is a fun game you can't say it isn't. However the thing wrong with it is, it's very repetative. It's missing something that adds something interesting to the game. So far it's just spawn in, kill, die respawn that's it. There's no leveling, upgrading, unlocking at all which is quite sad. It would make the game more interesting and would give the player something to work towards. The only time when you are going to have fun and ignore that the game is lacking fun features is when you play with 3 or more friends. That's when things get highly enjoyable and worth playing.PriceIn my opinion the price is perfect for what this game has to offer. It's not much. So if you and your buds have $5 in your bank/steam wallet and are looking for a fun game to hang out in. I will recommend this game. There's a huge amount of maps which you're able to download to have even more fun in.Pros- Great workshop (you can download custom character models/weapon skins)- Character, weapon editor and map editor.- Slightly competative when playing with a large group of friends.- Fun weapons.Cons- If you host your friends will have 150 to 300 ping playing.- Gets repetative after a while. (no leveling/unlockables meaning nothing to play towards)- Difficult character model editing (might want to check some tutorial vids on youtube towards that.)Personal Recommendation1. Must get.2. Recommended purchase3. Recommended purchase during sale.4. Not recommended unless heavily discounted.5. Not recommended."
